Summary: A low flying very bright almost circular object flew south for about 4 seconds then disappeared. I was on I-95 headed to Florida.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving with some of my family down to Florida on I-95. On not one, but TWO separate occasions I noticed the same low-flying, very bright object dart across the sky at dazzling speeds with no tail and then suddenly disappear. Everyone in my car was asleep but I woke them up to tell them the story. It was so absurdly noticeable that I expected there to be an uproar about it online but I only found one small article! It was very fast but I'm shocked that more people aren't asking questions.
